    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape and ready for its next big adventure. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as appreciated. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. Drop me a message if you want to come see it or take it for a spin. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
