    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis retains its signature balance with MacPherson struts up front and a sophisticated multi-link rear setup. Recent service includes a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement check. While it displays minor aesthetic patina from spirited use, the mechanical vitals remain stout, offering a visceral, analog connection to the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
