    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for 2018 Executive Sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. This vehicle is in solid condition, having been primarily garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, with only minor, expected imperfections such as a few light stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well that has been professionally touched up. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the charcoal leather seats show only minimal bolsters wear, and the interior has never been smoked in. All electronic features\u2014including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, supported by a comprehensive service history. We recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the tires and brakes have plenty of life remaining. This is an honest, dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive home with peace of mind. Full service records are available upon request.",
